<author>Patea</author>
<title>Ngaitie Kalvari-ah</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ngaitie Kalvari-a na lungkham ni khan,
 Dogal simsen lohte a hungkhawm ui;
 Kuo a na lungkhamna he nuom?
 Van meipin nang a hun bawm ui,
 Kalvari liepsak ui.

[V2]
 Amen, Amen Hallelujah Amen,
 Lei leh vanin Amen tiu hen;
 Tuisuohgiet leh khawvel cheng hin,
 Hallelui ti sawn hen.

[V3]
 2. Ngaitie, thihna nuoiseh in a thokit tai,
 Thihna suna khawpi lawp ngeilo kha;
 Kalvari pak lawpin leng ui,
 Thawkna sun in, zawhna pak ui;
 Buoina a um ta puoi.

[V4]
 3. Thihna luigal a aw Salem khawpi khu,
 Lalna gam pakcha hawihin a bawm ie,
 Ziechun phaiphuleng a tum ui,
 Zopa Lal lien a chawian ui;
 Pakna gi a dai puoi.</lyrics>
</song>